<h2>PSA Features</h2>
<ul>
	<li>Client/Company Management</li>
	<li>Detailed project information</li>
	<li>An hierarchial task lists</li>
	<li>Graphical Gantt charts</li>
	<li>A repository for project related files</li>
	<li>A contacts list</li>
